desc: 5-spoke wheel plus a bolt-on mounting tab — a two-part assembly
use: demonstrates multi-solid export; STEP and 3MF carry the wheel and the
use: bracket as two separate named bodies in one file, STL welds them
component wheel
rim_out  add  cyl:r40h12
rim_in   cut  cyl:r34h14   @0,0,-1
hub      add  cyl:r10h12
hubbore  cut  cyl:r4h14    @0,0,-1
spokes   add  box:w30d5h6  @0,0,3   polar:n5r21
component bracket
tab      add  box:w22d14h6  @51,0,0
hole     cut  cyl:r3.2h8    @56,0,-1
